    // =========================================================================
    // ⚙️ CONFIG - DUPLICATE REMOVED (ADR-252 Security Fix)
    // =========================================================================
    // 📅 Removed: 2026-03-20 — This was a DANGEROUS duplicate with open writes
    // 🔒 SECURITY: The first config block (above) has `allow write: if false`
    //    but this duplicate had `allow create, update, delete: if isAuthenticated()`
    //    Firestore uses most-permissive-wins, so ANY auth user could write config!
    // =========================================================================

    // =========================================================================
